text: The Shensi tree frog, Tsinling tree frog or Tsinling tree toad (Hyla tsinlingensis) is a frog from China. Scientists saw it between 930 and 1770 meters above sea level in Gansu, Shaanxi, Chongqing and in a few places in Anhui and Henan. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Shensi tree frog
